    <br />
    Go to below buttons to explore the data from API and save it to the databse.

</p>

<table class="table">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Candidates" class="btn btn-primary my-2">Look up Candidates</a>
